| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-0098 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8a237694-176d-5f6f-aca9-b79e82fe9e69"
